{"tid":1480821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"818唔帶gear? 咪 on9 啦你地","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:11:08.000Z","uid":305408,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4704721c2fa2912239ffbf8d2083695afef49369","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"屌你你班撚樣傻架？<br />\n<br />\n帶gear  有乜撚野問題<br />\n帶埋出去駛死？咪撚再俾班人帶風向話和理非唔需要gear<br />\n你老母臭閪 香港黎架 帶gear 係唔會觸犯任何法例<br />\n帶出去係以防有咩事要戴 ，唔係叫你著撚住去衝擊<br />\n<br />\n你點撚知班狗癲起上黎話集會有可疑人物<br />\n衝入去亂打人或者扔催淚蛋？<br />\n<br />\n仲有 唔撚該你地有隊友既就組隊 無既就唔好亂信陌生人，有人問起老閪都話有照應 <br />\n落單好撚危險<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cfaff8dbe319780250c1b34cc9e5de1008a834b4","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"3a51f7986376f5213cf67713a28b1d2ac4e71349","tid":1480821,"uid":5809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"full gear出動，出核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>「Join us or Burn with us」</code><br />\n<code>「對抗暴政，否則攬炒」</code>"},{"pid":"049604a8540bb70d132ec781c041da94eeb8b7bc","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8119e0fcd8f0f07d92cda539a00a2e7f6d66fa80","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"0549e858a32be467c23978e9e9d41b4beb189149","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"aa38de7e980ee2d35a2fbe90bea07080e8e4e130","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"46f95cbd9b3ede2ec8704532ba683076077a34c1","tid":1480821,"uid":305408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:58:22.000Z","m